broodKernel v4.x 
Branch: 3.4.x
Current Version: broodKernel v4.1
Current Branch: 3.4.46

For Ariesve (i9001) or all other msm7x30 devices with some modifications.

Site:
www.broodplank.net

Topic:
http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1737717





Requirements:
- Linaro Toolchain (Cortex A8 Optimized) from Christopher83 extracted at ~/toolchains/linaro
- Packages to build kernel



Download:
- git clone https://github.com/broodplank/samsung-kernel-msm7x30 -b cm-10.1 ~/broodKernel
- cd ~/broodKernel



Initial Setup & Running Xconfig:
- ./xconfig



Building:
- ./build_clean 
or
- ./build_dirty



